            "processed": "<p>A python package for background and shading correction of optical microscopy images</p><p><br><span>BaSiCPy is a python package for background and shading correction of optical microscopy images. It is developed based on the Matlab version of </span><a href=\"https://github.com/marrlab/BaSiC\">BaSiC</a><span> tool with major improvements in the algorithm.</span></p>",
